### ============================================================
###  ERP - Flujo completo: Creación de Producto y Stock
###  Orden de ejecución: sigue la numeración (1 → 19)
### ============================================================
###
###  Microservicios:
###    Catalogs  → http://localhost:5181
###    Inventory → http://localhost:5010
###
###  Antes de correr:
###    1. docker compose up -d          (RabbitMQ + Seq)
###    2. cd src/Catalogs/Catalogs.WebApi   && dotnet run
###    3. cd src/Inventory/Inventory.WebApi && dotnet run
###
### ============================================================

@catalogs  = http://localhost:5181/api/v1
@inventory = http://localhost:5010/api/v1

# ── IDs que se copian de las respuestas anteriores ────────────
@brandId      = 70f6627c-a133-4a97-821e-edce04097ef5
@categoryId   = d8198b74-9e04-447e-b2b0-1f66d563c88b
@productId    = 69973bd3-a270-46b4-b2f1-c68ebd53a791
@warehouseId  = <pega-el-id-de-la-respuesta-4>
@locationId   = <pega-el-id-de-la-respuesta-5>
@reservationId = <pega-el-id-de-la-respuesta-9>


### ============================================================
###  CATALOGS
### ============================================================

### 1. Crear Marca
# @name createBrand
POST {{catalogs}}/brands
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "TechPro",
  "description": "Línea de productos tecnológicos"
}

###

### 2. Crear Categoría
# @name createCategory
POST {{catalogs}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Electrónicos",
  "description": "Equipos y accesorios electrónicos",
  "parentCategoryId": null
}

###

### 3. Crear Producto
# @name createProduct
# Requiere: brandId y categoryId del paso 1 y 2
POST {{catalogs}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "LAPTOP-TECHPRO-007",
  "name": "Laptop TechPro Prueba 7\"",
  "description": "Laptop de alto rendimiento para profesionales #7",
  "price": 1299.99,
  "currency": "USD",
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "brandId": "{{brandId}}"
}

###

### 4. Consultar Productos
GET {{catalogs}}/products
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Consultar Producto por ID
GET {{catalogs}}/products/{{productId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Cambiar Precio del Producto
PATCH {{catalogs}}/products/{{productId}}/price
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "newPrice": 1199.99,
  "currency": "USD"
}

###

### 7. Activar Producto
PATCH {{catalogs}}/products/{{productId}}/activate

###


### ============================================================
###  INVENTORY
### ============================================================

### 8. Sync manual del producto en Inventory
# ⚠️  Úsalo si el evento ProductCreated no llegó a Inventory
#     (p.ej. Inventory no estaba corriendo cuando se creó el producto).
#     Requiere: productId, brandId, categoryId del paso 1-3.
POST {{inventory}}/products/sync
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "sku": "LAPTOP-TECHPRO-001",
  "name": "Laptop TechPro 15\"",
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "brandId": "{{brandId}}"
}

###

### 10. Crear Almacén
# @name createWarehouse
POST {{inventory}}/warehouses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "ALM-CENTRAL-01",
  "name": "Almacén Central",
  "description": "Bodega principal de operaciones"
}

###

### 11. Agregar Ubicación al Almacén
# @name addLocation
# Requiere: warehouseId del paso 10
POST {{inventory}}/warehouses/{{warehouseId}}/locations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "warehouseId": "{{warehouseId}}",
  "aisle": "A",
  "rack": "01",
  "level": "1",
  "name": "Estante A-01-1"
}

###

### 12. Consultar Almacenes
GET {{inventory}}/warehouses
Accept: application/json

###

### 13. Recibir Mercancía (Receipt)
# Requiere: paso 8 (sync), paso 10 (warehouse), paso 11 (location)
# Si usaste el sync manual (paso 8), ya puedes recibir directamente.
# Requiere: warehouseId (paso 10), locationId (paso 11), productId (paso 3)
POST {{inventory}}/stock/receive
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "warehouseId": "{{warehouseId}}",
  "reference": "PO-2026-0001",
  "notes": "Primera recepción de laptops",
  "date": "2026-03-30T10:00:00Z",
  "lines": [
    {
      "productId": "{{productId}}",
      "locationId": "{{locationId}}",
      "lotId": null,
      "quantity": 50,
      "unitCost": 850.00
    }
  ]
}

###

### 14. Consultar Stock
GET {{inventory}}/stock
Accept: application/json

###

### 15. Consultar Kardex del Producto
GET {{inventory}}/stock/kardex/{{productId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 16. Reservar Stock (para un pedido de venta)
# @name createReservation
POST {{inventory}}/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "warehouseId": "{{warehouseId}}",
  "locationId": "{{locationId}}",
  "lotId": null,
  "quantity": 5,
  "salesOrderId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "expiresAt": "2026-04-30T23:59:59Z"
}

###

### 17. Cancelar Reserva
PATCH {{inventory}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}/cancel

###

### 18. Emitir Mercancía (Issue / Despacho)
POST {{inventory}}/stock/issue
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "warehouseId": "{{warehouseId}}",
  "reference": "SO-2026-0001",
  "notes": "Despacho por orden de venta",
  "date": "2026-03-30T14:00:00Z",
  "lines": [
    {
      "productId": "{{productId}}",
      "locationId": "{{locationId}}",
      "lotId": null,
      "quantity": 3
    }
  ]
}

###

### 19. Ajuste de Inventario
POST {{inventory}}/stock/adjust
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "warehouseId": "{{warehouseId}}",
  "locationId": "{{locationId}}",
  "lotId": null,
  "newQuantity": 45,
  "unitCost": 850.00,
  "reference": "ADJ-2026-001",
  "notes": "Ajuste por conteo físico"
}

###
